@StackShare.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5095

### Health Check
GET {{StackShare.API_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Register User
POST {{StackShare.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123"
}

###

### Login User
POST {{StackShare.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

###

### Get User Profile (requires JWT token from login)
GET {{StackShare.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Generate MCP Token
POST {{StackShare.API_HostAddress}}/api/users/me/mcp-tokens
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "My Development Token"
}

###

### List MCP Tokens
GET {{StackShare.API_HostAddress}}/api/users/me/mcp-tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Revoke MCP Token (replace {{token_id}} with actual token ID)
DELETE {{StackShare.API_HostAddress}}/api/users/me/mcp-tokens/{{token_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###
